@pjljvandelaar -- I've diagnosed the crash on the instances in `z3str3.crash.zip`. I will upstream a patch once I have verified this doesn't break on other instances.

The crash in `z3str3.process12.zip` occurs with the sequence solver as well, and in the debugger it seems to be happening in the rewriter. 

